{"tid":2045973,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"五大校長發聲明支持國安法","createTime":"2020-06-01T06:28:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:42:31.000Z","uid":89543,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"b1ddcaeeca61b0d936d3dc44b9b72a8b04c27cff","tid":2045973,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:28:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/101891495_1463198477205549_7508489134269267968_o.jpg?_nc_cat=101&amp;_nc_sid=730e14&amp;_nc_ohc=yG6ujtrwae4AX-T0uKV&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg1-1.fna&amp;oh=19ad806d09004942a03fff2ef8d6411d&amp;oe=5EF9C55F\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg1-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F101891495_1463198477205549_7508489134269267968_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D101%26_nc_sid%3D730e14%26_nc_ohc%3DyG6ujtrwae4AX-T0uKV%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg1-1.fna%26oh%3D19ad806d09004942a03fff2ef8d6411d%26oe%3D5EF9C55F&h=4d46385b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【五大校長聲明】當中又提到，珍惜基本法所保障的言論、新聞、出版及集會自由等權利，會一如既往堅守學術自由。八間資助大學中，科技大學、浸會大學及城市大學校長未有一同發表聲明<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞 #OTT #國安法 #嶺大 #鄭國漢 #中大 #段崇智 #教大 #張仁良 #理大 #滕錦光 #港大 #張翔"},{"pid":"4088b774ad0404b4918dfab88ef01134cee34a47","tid":2045973,"uid":89543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:28:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4498c8270a17274c314ef25b2261a7a725b872b","tid":2045973,"uid":38737,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:29:05.000Z","msg":"全部都係垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"deb7ae91f0f3dda627075c8aa2886d8ef6e02ae7","tid":2045973,"uid":279981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T06:29:07.000Z","msg":"最紅嘅開大呢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6eb57faf961437846223a19606393258436e8941","tid":2045973,"uid":89543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-